      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a module for our leadership training program. We want to give our senior execs some guidance on grooming and personal presentation for high-stakes boardroom meetings. Basically, how can they make sure their appearance projects maximum authority and professionalism? Any general tips or standard guidelines you can suggest?",
